## Context

This project uses **OpenSecKit V4** with hub-and-spokes architecture.

### System Model (Hub) - Always Read First
- **Index**: `.osk/system-model/index.yaml` (~200 lines, quick orientation)
- **Full sections**: `.osk/system-model/*.yaml` (load as needed)

### Outputs (Spokes)
- **Compliance**: `.osk/comply/`
- **Specifications**: `.osk/specs/`

