{% if command.part -%}
## Part

This command is part of the **{{ command.part | upper }}** workflow.
{% if command.part == "discover" -%}
- Discover commands build the system model (hub)
- Output goes to `.osk/system-model/`
{% elif command.part == "comply" -%}
- Comply commands assess compliance (spoke)
- Consumes system model, outputs to `.osk/comply/`
{% elif command.part == "secure" -%}
- Secure commands implement shift-left security (spoke)
- Consumes system model, outputs to `.osk/specs/`
{% endif %}
{% endif %}

